    <h3>Translation notes</h3>
    <p>Bisection is the constructive content of IVT. The sampling approach to EVT is not a proof; it misses the actual extremum by up to the sampling resolution. The real theorems depend on completeness and compactness, which have no computational shortcut.</p>

